    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo001.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、千紗ちゃんも\n大事な人に本音を言えないことがあったの？",
      "startTime": 2.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、私のお姉ちゃんもアイドルなんだけどね\n前に、二人でユニットを組んだことがあって",
      "startTime": 11.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "生まれた時からずっと一緒だったから\nきっと息もぴったりなんだろうなって思ってた",
      "startTime": 18.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お互いに譲り合ってうまくいかなくて……",
      "startTime": 22.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "大好きで尊敬しているお姉ちゃんに「私はこうしたい」\nって本音がなかなか言えなかった",
      "startTime": 32.0000012716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo002.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……\nお姉さんにはちゃんと本音を伝えられたの？",
      "startTime": 37.300000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "うん。とっても勇気が必要だったけど……\n伝えたおかげで、いろんなことがうまくいったんだ",
      "startTime": 45.2333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんだ！　良かった",
      "startTime": 49.1333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo004.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだか、サニピがあんなに\nキラキラしてる理由が分かったかも",
      "startTime": 54.600000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　どういうこと……？",
      "startTime": 57.300000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo005.m4a",
      "text": "不思議だったんだ。サニピは明るくてすっごく可愛い\nでも、なんかそれだけじゃない気がするなーって",
      "startTime": 64.5333335877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo006.m4a",
      "text": "きっとみんな、千紗ちゃんみたいにいろんなことを\n乗り越えて今があるんだよね",
      "startTime": 71.7333335877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo007.m4a",
      "text": "五人とも、どこか強い芯を持ってる\nだからサニピは、あんなにキラキラしてるんだなって",
      "startTime": 78.2666679383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……ありがとう\n私もね、Aqoursを見て同じことを感じてたよ",
      "startTime": 85.0666679383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo008.m4a",
      "text": "私達って、実は似た者同士なのかもね",
      "startTime": 89.933334605,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5733.3333332999955,
          "startTime": 95.6666679383
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "うん、そうかも\n……あ",
      "startTime": 96.8000012716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_youroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "youroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo009.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そういえばまだ料理してなかったっけ\nよーし、すぐ作るから待っててね！",
      "startTime": 102.5000012716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――東京でのライブ当日",
      "startTime": 106.8666679383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo010.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん、すっごく似合ってる！　可愛い！",
      "startTime": 110.0666699726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……曜ちゃんもとっても似合ってるよ\nあ、曜ちゃん……もしかして、緊張してる？",
      "startTime": 117.9925337291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo011.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあね、だってあのサニピと一緒のステージに\n立つんだから",
      "startTime": 126.6333391825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ、今日はお揃いの衣装だし\n一緒のグループの気持ちでやろう？",
      "startTime": 132.1000058491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo012.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん……えへへ、ありがとう\nじゃあ、一緒にいつものやつやろっか！",
      "startTime": 138.9000058491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "全速前進、ヨーソロー！",
      "startTime": 142.2333391825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo014.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、緊張がほぐれてきたー！",
      "startTime": 147.333333079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　あ、さくらちゃん\nえっと、これは曜ちゃんに教えてもらった挨拶で……",
      "startTime": 154.1999997456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yo",
      "speakerName": "渡辺曜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-yo015.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん、せっかくだからサニピのみんなとも\n一緒にやってみない？",
      "startTime": 162.5666694641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yo_01_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも……うん、その方が元気が出るかも",
      "startTime": 164.3333310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
